<p>I ran a Claude Code session for ten days.</p>

<p>Not ten days straight. Ten days of real work ŌĆö building, iterating, shipping posts, wiring up interactive components, updating docs. The kind of work I do every week now. When it was done, I exported the session data and went looking for something I couldnŌĆÖt quite name.</p>

