<p>426 messages. 13.1 million tokens. And when I broke down what was actually happening in those messages ŌĆö not just ŌĆ£user sends prompt, assistant respondsŌĆØ but <em>what each message was doing</em> ŌĆö something uncomfortable came into focus.</p>

